task.summary: Default task
Standardize project structure, move sql code to resources directory.
Increase the effectiveness of stat increases and skill increases for Stun spell. Fixes #43
Fix libs folder reference
Add transaction.auto_close_session property to DB properties. Fix issue with removing infection crud inventory items on infection loss.
Remove minimum c3p0 connections. Add timeout for idle connections.
Increase the minimum damage of flame spell. Fixes #65
Reduce the max random effect and increase the base minimum static effect of treatment kits. Fixes #59
Log client logins and logouts to DB. Completes #37

Add comments to all abilities to assist with the external documentation efforts.
Also fixed bugs with the teleport spells and light spell.

Fix GetResearchCategoriesAvailableForCraftAndLevel.sql: Search for options at and below player research level instead of exactly at that level.
Refresh ability: Use enhancement affinity instead of holy.
Fix comment for Flame
Add details to the comment for Refresh
Add details to the Blind ability comment
Update database backup file.
Explain the Poison custom effect in the Poison spell comment.
Fix typo in the Piercing Toss comment
Update database backup.
Update module file. Added two versions: 1.69 (stable) and 1.74 (experimental)
Confer bonus inventory slots for STR upgrades. Fixes #71
Update module files. Update SQL script backup. Add 2DA files to git. Fixes #75
Regenerate ability: Increase amount to 2 at 3 wisdom modifier. decrease interval to 5 seconds at 6 wisdom modifier. Fixes #68
Update module file for 1.74. This includes changes to use the new NWNX Java API.
Migrate a lot of NWNX_Funcs to the new NWNX_Admin and NWNX_Creature plugins.
Update references to the old NWNX_Funcs Start/Stop GUI timing bar to use the new NWNX_Player ones.
Update paths to nwnx2.ini file (will be changed soon since EE no longer uses the file), change path to look for jar files.
Remove old NWNX2 files, add database.ini and update DataAccess to check this file instead. Also fix the API for Start/Stop GUI timing bars in the NWNX_Player plugin.
Update event handler script for setting area scripts.
Update API for start/stop timing bars. Remove unused methods from old NWNX API.
Replace GetConversation with new GetDialogResref method. Update usages. Deleted NWNX_Funcs_Old.java
Update database backup.
Migrate calls to OnFeatUsed and OnItemUsed events.
Remove old unused DM events.
Add event methods for OnCastSpell. Move magic strings into constants. Update OnCastSpell script.
Update JVM script name and variables to match their new standards. Remove some dead code that doesn't need migration.
Update database backup.
Update database backup.
Update database backup.
Update hook for the OnAttack event (now called OnCombatRoundStart). Update the database.ini config file header. Fix name for the jar file.
Update the nwnx jar file library.
Remove the last dependency on the old NWNX_Events. Fix crash issue with using items. Remove SimTools from the 1.74 module.

Rework durability system to use local variables instead of item properties. Change calculations on damage loss in ranged combat system. Change calculations for repair kits. Remove most random factors from durability loss. Also remove the CD key management options from the rest menu (no longer needed in EE).
